mpConfigMaxAudioMixCount.name: mpConfigMaxAudioMixCount
mpConfigMaxAudioMixCount.description: Maximum number of participants allowed in the audio mix.

mpConfigMaxVideoMixCount.name: mpConfigMaxVideoMixCount
mpConfigMaxVideoMixCount.description: Maximum number of participants allowed in the video mix.

mpConferenceTable.name: mpConferenceTable
mpConferenceTable.description: This table contains information about running conferences. It is a list of conference entries. The number of entries equals to the number of running conferences.

mpConferenceTableEntry.name: mpConferenceTableEntry
mpConferenceTableEntry.description: It contains objects that describe a specific conference.

mpConferenceConferenceId.name: mpConferenceConferenceId
mpConferenceConferenceId.description: The conference identifier as specified in ITU-T H.323V2 specification.

mpConferenceAudioNoiseThreshold.name: mpConferenceAudioNoiseThreshold
mpConferenceAudioNoiseThreshold.description: This value represents the audio power level above which the signal is detected as speech.

mpConferenceLipSyncEnable.name: mpConferenceLipSyncEnable
mpConferenceLipSyncEnable.description: This value indicates rather the lip syncronization adjustments are performed.

mpConferenceParticipantsTable.name: mpConferenceParticipantsTable
mpConferenceParticipantsTable.description: This table contains information about conference participants. It is a list of participant entries. The number of entries equals the number of participants for all conferences.

mpConferenceParticipantsTableEntry.name: mpConferenceParticipantsTableEntry
mpConferenceParticipantsTableEntry.description: It contains objects that describe a specific conference participant.

mpConferenceParticipantsTableIndex.name: mpConferenceParticipantsTableIndex
mpConferenceParticipantsTableIndex.description: An arbitrary index to this table. This index is one for the first participant for every given conference. It is incremented by one for each subsequent participant of the same conference. The last index for a particular conference is equal to the number of participants for that conference.

mpConferenceParticipantsEndpointId.name: mpConferenceParticipantsEndpointId
mpConferenceParticipantsEndpointId.description: The H.323 id of this participant as described in ITU-T H.323V2 specification.

mpConferenceParticipantsTransmitAudioSta.name: mpConferenceParticipantsTransmitAudioState
mpConferenceParticipantsTransmitAudioSta.description: This value indicates the state of transmitted audio: normal - transmit normal audio toneGeneration - transmit test tone mute - transmit silence audio off - no audio is transmitted

mpConferenceParticipantsReceiveAudioStat.name: mpConferenceParticipantsReceiveAudioState
mpConferenceParticipantsReceiveAudioStat.description: This value indicates the state of received audio: normal - receive normal audio loopBack - received audio presented unchanged to the transmitter block - received audio is not part of the mix off - no audio is received

mpConferenceParticipantsTransmitVideoSta.name: mpConferenceParticipantsTransmitVideoState
mpConferenceParticipantsTransmitVideoSta.description: This value indicates the state of transmitted video: on - normal video is transmitted off - no video is transmitted.

mpConferenceParticipantsReceiveVideoStat.name: mpConferenceParticipantsReceiveVideoState
mpConferenceParticipantsReceiveVideoStat.description: This value indicates the state of transmitted video: normal - normal video is received block - received video is not displayed off - no video is transmitted.

mpConferenceParticipantsLoudnessMeasurem.name: mpConferenceParticipantsLoudnessMeasurement
mpConferenceParticipantsLoudnessMeasurem.description: This is the current loudness measurement value in dB.

mpConferenceParticipantsVoiceActivity.name: mpConferenceParticipantsVoiceActivity
mpConferenceParticipantsVoiceActivity.description: This value is True when the speech is detected.

mpConferenceParticipantsInputAudioGain.name: mpConferenceParticipantsInputAudioGain
mpConferenceParticipantsInputAudioGain.description: This value reflects the current input volume adjustment in dB.

mpConferenceParticipantsOutputAudioGain.name: mpConferenceParticipantsOutputAudioGain
mpConferenceParticipantsOutputAudioGain.description: This value reflects the current output volume adjustment in dB.

mpConferenceParticipantsMaxAudioEncoderP.name: mpConferenceParticipantsMaxAudioEncoderPayloadSize
mpConferenceParticipantsMaxAudioEncoderP.description: The maximum size of payload in ms.

mpConferenceParticipantsMaxAudioDecoderP.name: mpConferenceParticipantsMaxAudioDecoderPayloadSize
mpConferenceParticipantsMaxAudioDecoderP.description: The maximum size of payload in ms.

mpConferenceParticipantsTotalPacketsTran.name: mpConferenceParticipantsTotalPacketsTransmitted
mpConferenceParticipantsTotalPacketsTran.description: The total number of transmitted packets.

mpConferenceParticipantsTotalPacketsRece.name: mpConferenceParticipantsTotalPacketsReceived
mpConferenceParticipantsTotalPacketsRece.description: The total number of received packets.

mpConferenceParticipantsInvalidPacketErr.name: mpConferenceParticipantsInvalidPacketErrors
mpConferenceParticipantsInvalidPacketErr.description: The total number of packets with invalid packet errors.

mpConferenceParticipantsLateAudioPackets.name: mpConferenceParticipantsLateAudioPacketsDropped
mpConferenceParticipantsLateAudioPackets.description: The total number of packets that arrived too late to be processed.

mpConferenceParticipantsReceivedSilenceP.name: mpConferenceParticipantsReceivedSilencePackets
mpConferenceParticipantsReceivedSilenceP.description: The total number of silence packets that were received.

mpConferenceParticipantsSilencePacketsGe.name: mpConferenceParticipantsSilencePacketsGenerated
mpConferenceParticipantsSilencePacketsGe.description: The total number of silence packets that were generated.

mpConferenceParticipantsVideoFrameRate.name: mpConferenceParticipantsVideoFrameRate
mpConferenceParticipantsVideoFrameRate.description: This value represents the current measured frame rate received.

mpConferenceParticipantsFullPictureCount.name: mpConferenceParticipantsFullPictureCounter
mpConferenceParticipantsFullPictureCount.description: This value represents the number of full image pictures received.

mpConferenceGlobalAudioMixTable.name: mpConferenceGlobalAudioMixTable
mpConferenceGlobalAudioMixTable.description: This table contains information about conference participants that are present in a global audio mix. It is a list of participant entries. The number of entries equals to the sum of all audio mix participants in all conferences.

mpConferenceGlobalAudioMixTableEntry.name: mpConferenceGlobalAudioMixTableEntry
mpConferenceGlobalAudioMixTableEntry.description: It contains objects that describe the participants.

mpConferenceGlobalAudioMixTableIndex.name: mpConferenceGlobalAudioMixTableIndex
mpConferenceGlobalAudioMixTableIndex.description: An arbitrary index to this table. This index is one for the first participant for every given conference. It is incremented by one for each subsequent participant of the same conference. The last index for a particular conference is equal to the number of participants for that conference.

mpConferenceGlobalAudioMixTerminalIdenti.name: mpConferenceGlobalAudioMixTerminalIdentifier
mpConferenceGlobalAudioMixTerminalIdenti.description: The H.323 id of this participant as described in ITU-T H.323V2 specification.

mpConferenceGlobalVideoMixTable.name: mpConferenceGlobalVideoMixTable
mpConferenceGlobalVideoMixTable.description: This table contains information about conference participants that are present in a global video mix. It is a list of participant entries. The number of entries equals to the sum of all video mix participants in all conferences.

mpConferenceGlobalVideoMixTableEntry.name: mpConferenceGlobalVideoMixTableEntry
mpConferenceGlobalVideoMixTableEntry.description: It contains objects that describe the participants.

mpConferenceGlobalVideoMixTableIndex.name: mpConferenceGlobalVideoMixTableIndex
mpConferenceGlobalVideoMixTableIndex.description: An arbitrary index to this table. This index is one for the first participant for every given conference. It is incremented by one for each subsequent participant of the same conference. The last index for a particular conference is equal to the number of participants for that conference.

mpConferenceGlobalVideoMixTerminalIdenti.name: mpConferenceGlobalVideoMixTerminalIdentifier
mpConferenceGlobalVideoMixTerminalIdenti.description: The H.323 id of this participant as described in ITU-T H.323V2 specification.

mpMIBCompliance.description: The set of objects required for compliance.
